<HEADLINE>
FOR YUGOSLAVS, THE PAST KEEPS GETTING BETTER 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating) (The Week in Review) 
 By STEVEN ERLANGER    
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
