<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CHINA INVITES RIGHTS ACTIVIST IN TO DISCUSS POLITICAL PRISONERS
 &HT;    (550&AMP;ADD)
 &HT;    With Photo.
