<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-01 17:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2572 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w BC-CELL-PHONE-SAFETY-HNS     05-01 0726
