<P>
   CELL-PHONE-SAFETY (Washington) _ Scientists are launching a new
series of studies to determine whether radiation from cell phones
sparks maladies such as leukemia, cancer, birth defects,
reproductive ailments in women and diseases in children. By ERIC
ROSENBERG. (Already filed.)
</P>
